PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Montez STOVALL, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 158557
COA: 342440 Supreme Court of Michigan. November 28, 2018

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the motion for the temporary admission of out-of-state attorney Marsha L. Levick to appear and practice in this case under MCR 8.126(A) is GRANTED.
